<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.5.4">
<l>aṟiyātārk kāṉāya ṉākippō yāyppāṭi</l>
<l>uṟiyār naṟuveṇṇe yuṇṭukantāṉ kāṇēṭī</l>
<l>uṟiyār naṟuveṇṇe yuṇṭukanta poṉvayiṟṟuk</l>
<l>keṟinī rulakaṉaittu meytātāl cāḻalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See, Friend! Going to [those] ignorant folk as a boy herder,</l>
<l>He enjoyed eating fragrant butter that filled the pot nets in the herder village.</l>
<l>For the golden belly that enjoyed eating fragrant butter</l>
<l rend="indent">that filled the pot nets,</l>
<l>The entire earth with the crashing seas was not enough. Cāḻalē!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
